reviewText:
The Videos are a reflection of that time! Great surfing from some of the best players of that generation! My favorite is (Sundance) it has Lot's of hot young hawaiian surf stars! Featuring the South and North shores of Oahu and neighboring islands when the winter and summer swells sweep through!
The film quality is decent but could be a bit better.  Overall it's a great package deal!
